      "name": "Hemolysis index validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) values compared against pre-revision experimental measurements at 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3%; maximum point-wise deviation 14.1%. Validation was performed using the pre-revision experimental dataset without re-running experiments against the updated model geometry. Acceptable per assessment team's materiality judgement."
